      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 26,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/mavam/pi-terminal-theme/blob/8755ef65b16bd9996decd003edd59dade42a102a/README.md",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/mavam/pi-terminal-theme/raw/8755ef65b16bd9996decd003edd59dade42a102a/README.md",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/mavam/pi-terminal-theme/contents/README.md?ref=8755ef65b16bd9996decd003edd59dade42a102a",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,26 @@\n+# \ud83d\udda5\ufe0f pi-terminal-theme\n+\n+Your terminal colors are fine. Stop overriding them.\n+\n+This [pi](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/tree/main/packages/coding-agent)\n+theme maps UI colors to ANSI `0..15`. That's it.\n+\n+## \ud83d\udce6 Install\n+\n+```bash\n+pi install git:github.com/mavam/pi-terminal-theme\n+```\n+\n+## \ud83c\udfa8 Use\n+\n+Pick `terminal` in `/settings` \u2192 `theme`, or:\n+\n+```json\n+{\n+  \"theme\": \"terminal\"\n+}\n+```\n+\n+## \ud83d\udcc4 License\n+\n+[MIT](LICENSE)"
    },
